    "name": "Marshal Dedication",
    "prerequisite": "trained in *Diplomacy* or *Intimidation*; trained in martial weapons",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You\u2019ve combined your social skills and combat training to become a talented combat leader. Choose Diplomacy or Intimidation. You become trained in that skill or become an expert if you were already trained in it.  \n  \nIn addition, while you\u2019re conscious, you\u2019re surrounded by a marshal\u2019s aura in a 15-foot emanation. Your aura has the emotion, mental, and visual traits and grants you and allies in the aura a +1 status bonus to saving throws against fear.",
    "traits": [
